## What's Done

### Modal (Login Signup Modal component)
- 4 steps: email entry, account type (Privat/Erhverv), registration, login
- Split headings (dark + orange italic accent) on all steps
- Step 2: centered, Privat/Erhverv cards with person/briefcase icon assets
- Step 3: email, name, phone, password with eye icon, checkboxes
- Step 4: welcome + name, lighter green login button (#BCF0DA)
- Right column: subheading with dash, heading with swirl underline, USPs with check-circle assets + GRATIS badge, review card, CS team photos, Trustpilot widget
- All icons as proper Webflow Image elements with asset IDs (no hardcoded CDN URLs)
- Responsive: mobile hides right column, full-screen single column

### Navigation (Navigation component)
- Desktop: top utility bar, main nav with mega menus (Erhverv/Privat hover)
- Mobile: sticky nav, hamburger menu with two-level accordion (categories → products)
- "Log ind" opens modal, "Opret en gratis konto" as orange CTA button in mobile menu

### Footer (Footer Figma component)
- All placeholder texts replaced with Figma content
- Logos corrected (Legal Desk white, Jurio neg)
- Social icons: Facebook + LinkedIn white SVGs

### Scripts (8 total — all functional, no visual hacks)
