2. mega_menu_hover — Desktop mega menu hover behavior
3. modal_styles_inject v1.6.0 — Modal CSS layout + responsive
4. nav_responsive_css v1.8.0 — Mobile nav CSS + hamburger styling
5. modal_open_close v1.1.0 — Modal open/close + Escape key
6. modal_step_navigation v1.2.0 — Step switching + form validation
7. modal_email_prefill v1.1.0 — Carries email between steps
8. nav_hamburger_js v2.4.0 — Hamburger button + mobile accordion

