### Architecture notes
- Modal lives as a component instance on the body (outside nav-wrapper)
- Auth flow: Webflow modal → Umbraco REST API → session cookie → redirect to app.legaldesk.dk
- All scripts are page-level (not site-level) on the Home page
- When adding the modal to other pages, apply the same scripts via upsert_page_script

