## Working Preferences
- Never hardcode CDN URLs — always use Webflow Image elements with asset IDs
- Extract SVGs from Figma, save locally, user uploads to Webflow assets
- Always prefer proper fixes over workarounds — ask user for manual help when MCP can't do it
- After MCP reconnection, always re-check element state before creating anything
